page.title: 13Plants
page.content: {Plants}growing in the area include: {River-side-}Giant Hogweed,Tansy,Indian Balsm,Comfrey,Butter Burr,Ramsoms and Yarrow. {Wetland-}Ragged Robin,Water Plantain Fue Flowered Leek,Burr Weed Phragmytes Spotted Nothern Marsh Orchid. {Woodlands-}Primrose, Bluebells,Wood Anenome,Foxglove,Wood Sorrell,Celedine Forget-me-not, Harebell,Bracken,Ferns Stinkhorn and Flyagariic Fungi. {Fields-}Vipers Bugloss,Toadflax,Daises Dog Violet,Birdsfoot Trefoil,Ladies Smocks,Speedwell,Pineapple weed,Butter cup,Scarlet Pimpernel and common grasses,Fescues,Timothys and Bents. {Hedgerows-}Fumatory,Honeysuckle,Cow Parsley,Crosswort,Ladies Bedstraw,Dead nettle,Campion,MeadowCranesbill,Garlic Wild Rose,Vetch,Yellow Archangel, Rose Bay Willow Herb.
